      <a href="https://loveoahu.org/overview/7-day-itinerary/"><h3 class="country">Hawaii 2021</h3></a>
     <img src='https://i.postimg.cc/qvVxM5BB/hawaii.jpg' width=200px height=250px>
  <img src='https://i.postimg.cc/c1j5NhVT/poke.jpg' width=300px height=250px>
   <p class="text"> The sunset on the beach of Waikiki was the highlight of my trip. I also went surfing, ate world class poke and enjoyed eating the locally grown papaya. I tried spam musubi for the first time and loved it. I plan on one day going back.</p> 

  <a href="https://national-parks.org/ecuador/cotopaxi"><h3 class="country">Ecuador 2021</h3></a>
    <img src="https://i.postimg.cc/wTskzppb/ecuador.jpg" width="200"   height="240">
   <img src='https://i.postimg.cc/BbVWWG2C/ecuadorian-food.jpg' width='300' height='240'>
  <p class="text"> My cousin and I hiked the Cotopaxi, a volano in Ecuador. The elevation made the hike very hard but it was worth it. We arrived at the Jose Rivas Refuge tired and happy.</p>
  <a href="https://www.bookmundi.com/t/the-colosseum-a-must-visit"><h3 class="country">Italy 2019</h3></a>
   <img src= 'https://i.postimg.cc/W4SG8pGt/italy.jpg' width='200' height='240'>
   <img src= 'https://i.postimg.cc/zGCSLF3C/italian-food.jpg' width='200' height='240'>
  <p class="text">I absolutely loved my time in Italy. Some of my favorite memories included seeing David of MichelAngelo in Florence, listening to the history of the Colloseum and eating a ton of pasta.</p> 
